sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Proposal trade UI
    participant Preview as POST /api/trade/preview
    participant Execute as POST /api/trade/execute
    participant Auth as requireSessionUser
    participant DB as MongoDB

    User->>UI: Open /proposal/:id/trade
    UI->>Preview: proposalId, amountUsd, leverage, direction
    Preview->>DB: find proposal by id
    DB-->>Preview: proposal trade fields
    Preview->>Preview: validate leverage, entry price, stop loss, fee, slippage
    Preview-->>UI: risk preview, warnings, assumptions
    User->>UI: Confirm trade
    UI->>Execute: proposalId, amount, entryPrice, leverage, direction, riskPlan
    Execute->>Auth: requireSessionUser(request)
    Auth-->>Execute: walletAddress, userId
    Execute->>DB: find user by walletAddress
    Execute->>DB: find executable proposal
    Execute->>DB: start transaction
    Execute->>DB: check open perp_position for same proposal
    alt Existing open position
        DB-->>Execute: duplicate found
        Execute-->>UI: 409 already open
    else Executable
        Execute->>DB: insert trade_executions
        Execute->>DB: insert perp_positions
        Execute->>DB: update proposal status EXECUTED
        Execute->>DB: insert proposal_decisions
        Execute->>DB: commit transaction
        Execute-->>UI: execution and positionId
        UI->>UI: navigate to positions or show fill state
    end
    %% thiếu dữ liệu: execute route tao demo txHash, khong thay tich hop on-chain settlement thuc
